    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a reliable daily driver for someone looking for a solid value. While the engine and transmission are functioning properly, the car shows clear signs of its age, including some noticeable scratches and minor dings on the exterior body. Inside, the upholstery has some visible wear and staining from regular use, and a few of the plastic trim pieces show some aging. It runs and drives fine, though a buyer should expect to address some minor mechanical maintenance items in the near future, such as brake pad replacement and new tires.",
