      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this distinguished vehicle, meticulously maintained and representing an exceptional value proposition within its class. This specimen exhibits the pride of ownership expected of a premium pre-owned motorcar, offering a seamless blend of performance and reliability. Thoroughly inspected and prepared for its next owner, it remains a testament to enduring quality and engineering excellence.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
