    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty car, and she\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape\u2014super reliable and definitely has plenty of adventures left in the tank! I\u2019ve taken good care of it, so it\u2019s ready for you to just hop in and go. It's the perfect fit for someone who wants a dependable ride that still looks great on the road. Feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to come take it for a spin!",
      "price": 32500.0,
